"If your contact has not kept in touch, expect the worst, Hydras." Her feline 
face plate was totally serious. Having seen either terminations, captures or 
defections in the past with this type of behavior. 

"But," her optics still upon him, "I promise that I shall stay in contact 
with you." 

Then on the map something seemed to grab her attention. She pulled away & 
padded up to the map to examine it further. Her optics narrowed. It seemed 
that it was showing... activity at the Maximal base. "Seems the Maximals & 
Autobots are biting off more than they can chew. Seems your plan has worked."
